    @Deprecated
private static class TransducerBuilder.DeprecatedTransducerForLimitingNumberOfCandidates<CandidateType>
extends Transducer<DawgNode,CandidateType>
    Restricts the number of spelling candidates for a query. This class is only intended as a temporary shim until I remove TransducerBuilder.maxCandidates from the next API.
    Since:
    2.1.2
